## Troubleshooting

**"jdeps not found"**
- Install JDK ≥ 11 (not just JRE)
- Check: `jdeps --version`

**"No .dot files found"**
- Compile your project first: `mvn compile` or `gradle compileJava`
- Generate .dot files manually with jdeps
- Or specify `--dot <directory>` explicitly

**"Module not found" errors**
- Reinstall: `pip install -e .`
- Check Python version: `python --version` (must be ≥ 3.9)

